@node "distribution" "IMPORTANT -- DISTRIBUTION "
@next "feature_list"
@prev "Main"
@{bg shine}Distribution of PolyGraph, PolyMeas & Pridat@{bg back}

@{b}@{fg shine}PolyGraph is (C) Dr.Werner Mayr 1992-1995.@{ub}@{fg text}

PolyGraph is SHAREWARE. It is NOT public domain. The @{"author" link "how_to_contact" 0} gives permission for
PolyGraph to be freely distributed providing that no commercial gain is made
from its distribution, and no modification is made to the original
distribution.

Organisations or people wishing to include PolyGraph on a coverdisk or CD-ROM
should contact me first to sort out the details. This EXCLUDES the AMINET CD-ROM
or Fred Fish CD-ROM collections.

@{b}DISCLAIMER@{ub}

This software is provided "as-is" and the author accepts no responsibility for
damage and/or loss of data/equipment resulting from the use of this software.
(not that it's very likely! ;-})

@{b}COST@{ub}

Only a few features of PolyGraph are crippled to allow you to appreciate the
program nearly to the full. If you keep PolyGraph for more than an evaluation
period and to get the full version on an original disk please send the shareware
fee to the author. You should print out the "@{"OrderForm" link "orderform" 0}"-file for that purpose,
fill it in and send it to me. Please send the fee either in cash, Eurocheque,
Postal Money Order or Money transfer to my account.


    Shareware fee:

